snippet.title: Home of the Yokai | Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Home of the Yokai is a creature collecting Eastern fantasy RPG featuring an expansive world filled with rich stories, interesting characters, and over nearly 300 unique Yokai. On your journey across the Land to become a Yokai Keeper you will traverse through uncharted lands, encounter many never-before seen Yokai, and form new friendships. Yet, a looming evil is spreading, and many Yokai are succumbing to its corruption. The peaceful lives at home of the Yokai are in jeopardy, are you ready for what is to come?
_______________________________________________________________
